{"id":643761,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/宪政学者张雪忠被警察带走，现已获释回家/","date":"2020-05-11T09:34:11Z","modified":"2020-05-11T17:12:08Z","title":"宪政学者张雪忠被警察带走，现已获释回家","content":"<p>更新：最新消息称，北京时间5月11日凌晨，张雪忠被释放回家。</p>\n<p>据悉，宪政学者、华东政法大学教师张雪忠在发出致全国人大公开信后，5月10日凌晨，在所住小区被警察带走，至目前为止没有任何消息。</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"張雪忠：從湖北大學梁艳萍教授直言賈禍談中國的言論自由\" width=\"1080\" height=\"810\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IpfHqskdOZM?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_643762\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-643762\" class=\"wp-image-643762\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/IMG_2607-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/IMG_2607-150x300.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/IMG_2607-512x1024.jpg 512w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/IMG_2607-768x1536.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/IMG_2607-1024x2048.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/05/IMG_2607.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-643762\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">图片来自社交媒体。</p></div>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">刚刚从上海朋友哪里获息，张雪忠现在在上海，上海警察正在砸张雪忠教授家的门，张雪忠教授很可能已经被上海恶警非法抓捕。中共恶警对正义人士的抓捕早已司空见惯，随着中共在世界各地的臭名招著，正义人士正在迎来曙光！ <a href=\"https://t.co/EqTUowCylL\">pic.twitter.com/EqTUowCylL</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 江雪 (@bmzxdqz1127) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bmzxdqz1127/status/1259599132966047744?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 10, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">转：关注张雪忠！5月10日凌晨1点，张雪忠教授在所住小区门口被警察带走，至目前为止没有任何消息，电话关机。 <a href=\"https://t.co/C78vKfMvN0\">pic.twitter.com/C78vKfMvN0</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 新高地官推 官网：https://www.newhighlandvision.com/ (@5xyxh) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/5xyxh/status/1259724148768677888?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 11, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"ZwP4pMXNDz\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e5%bc%a0%e9%9b%aa%e5%bf%a0%e8%87%b4%e5%8d%81%e4%b8%89%e5%b1%8a%e5%85%a8%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e4%b8%89%e6%ac%a1%e4%bc%9a%e8%ae%ae%e5%85%a8%e4%bd%93%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%80%e5%b0%81/\">张雪忠致十三届全国人大三次会议全体代表的一封信 #31</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《张雪忠致十三届全国人大三次会议全体代表的一封信 #31》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/05/%e5%bc%a0%e9%9b%aa%e5%bf%a0%e8%87%b4%e5%8d%81%e4%b8%89%e5%b1%8a%e5%85%a8%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%ba%e5%a4%a7%e4%b8%89%e6%ac%a1%e4%bc%9a%e8%ae%ae%e5%85%a8%e4%bd%93%e4%bb%a3%e8%a1%a8%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%80%e5%b0%81/embed/#?secret=ZwP4pMXNDz\" data-secret=\"ZwP4pMXNDz\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%AE%AA%E6%94%BF\">CDS档案 | 宪政</a></strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1019,"categories":[18271,38912,38920],"tags":[9050,10579,15238,9212]}